Stay Safe Online – Prevention Checklist
Never share your UPI PIN, OTP, or banking details with anyone.
Do not approve unknown UPI collect requests.
Always verify the identity of the caller before taking any action.
Avoid clicking on suspicious links received through SMS, email, or social media.
Use official apps and websites for online transactions only.
Enable two-factor authentication (2FA) wherever possible.
Regularly check your bank statements and transaction history.
Install apps only from trusted sources like Play Store or App Store.
Be cautious of offers that seem too good to be true.
For any fraud, immediately report at cybercrime.gov.in or call 1930 helpline.
